item.title: CVE-2023-33842|2023-06-22T01:34:35.994Z -- ibm -- spss%20modeler
item.description: IBM SPSS Modeler on Windows 17.0, 18.0, 18.2.2, 18.3, 18.4, and 18.5 requires the end user to have access to the server SSL key which could allow a local user to decrypt and obtain sensitive information. IBM X-Force ID: 256117.
